"{\"uid\": \"kpcw.org-park-city-2024-07-17-park-city-summit-county-seek-consultant-to-gameplan-for-2034-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Park City Mayor Nann Worel will be in the room when IOC officials vote to award the 2034 Winter Olympics on July 24 in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 125, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 9, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Olympic_Park\", \"score\": 0.9999967479300851, \"rank\": 3.252080424540809e-06, \"text\": \"Park City\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Olympic_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Olympic_Park\"}, {\"begin\": 52, \"end\": 55, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9559174758450816e-15, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 119, \"end\": 124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999990908088007, \"rank\": 9.091919763726691e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Salt Lake City is widely expected to be named host, as it is the only bid under consideration.\", \"from\": 126, \"to\": 220, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"score\": 0.9998304458197323, \"rank\": 0.00016947708244528423, \"text\": \"Salt Lake City\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Days later Worel will have the chance to experience the Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 222, \"to\": 294, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That'll kick off on July 26 with an opening ceremony in boats down the Seine.\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 372, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 366, \"end\": 371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999388136518453, \"rank\": 6.057052251775732e-05, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The mayor wasn't in town during the 2002 Games, which like the 2034 plan, includes sporting events in Summit and Wasatch counties.\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 504, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 487, \"end\": 503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasatch_County,_Utah\", \"score\": 0.9999999942233444, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wasatch counties\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasatch_County,_Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wasatch_County,_Utah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Because I have never experienced an Olympics, I think it's important that I go and experience the flow of it,\\\" Worel said.\", \"from\": 506, \"to\": 629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"How is it structured?\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How do people move around?\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 679, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How do people interact?\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 703, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How do they feed that many people that are going to be in town?\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What does security look like?\\\"\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 798, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Park City is spending $12,000 to send Mayor Worel to France.\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 800, \"end\": 809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Olympic_Park\", \"score\": 0.9999967479300851, \"rank\": 3.252080424540809e-06, \"text\": \"Park City\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Olympic_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Olympic_Park\"}, {\"begin\": 853, \"end\": 859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9428752150516776, \"rank\": 0.04641160590292167, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Summit County is also spending thousands to send county council chair Malena Stevens.\", \"from\": 862, \"to\": 947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 862, \"end\": 875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summit_County,_Ohio\", \"score\": 0.7763715306986965, \"rank\": 0.15794269515034517, \"text\": \"Summit County\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summit_County,_Ohio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summit_County,_Ohio\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She says the trip is important to stay engaged.\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have a really big opportunity through the Olympics to be able to accelerate some of our infrastructure improvements throughout the county, in particular in Kimball Junction and potentially on SR-248.\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1157, \"end\": 1173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Park_City,_Utah\", \"score\": 0.9999999805206701, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kimball Junction\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Park_City,_Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Park_City,_Utah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And if we are not at the table, if we are not showing up, if we are not engaging with the committee that is planning, I am afraid that we will be forgotten.\\\"\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To help prepare, Park City, Summit County and the Park City Chamber of Commerce are planning to submit a request for proposal on July 29 to find a consultant that can help them prepare for the 2034 Winter Games.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1377, \"end\": 1386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Olympic_Park\", \"score\": 0.9999967479300851, \"rank\": 3.252080424540809e-06, \"text\": \"Park City\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Olympic_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Olympic_Park\"}, {\"begin\": 1388, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summit_County,_Ohio\", \"score\": 0.7763715306986965, \"rank\": 0.15794269515034517, \"text\": \"Summit County\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summit_County,_Ohio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summit_County,_Ohio\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chamber CEO Jennifer Wesselhoff, who is also traveling to Paris, says the goal is to learn from other Olympic host communities.\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1631, \"end\": 1636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999990908088007, \"rank\": 9.091919763726691e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It may be a business, it may be an individual person,\\\" Wesselhoff said.\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It may be people who have experience with past Games, winter or summer.\", \"from\": 1775, \"to\": 1847, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So we will be spreading a wide net.\\\"\", \"from\": 1848, \"to\": 1884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wesselhoff said they hope to complete work with the consultant before state lawmakers convene early next year for the legislative session.\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 2024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In case there are items in that action plan that we feel like we need to begin advocating for right now related to the legislative session in January,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2026, \"to\": 2188, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It will be a fairly quick process, but we are including active public engagement and stakeholder engagement in that RFP.\\\"\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2311, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"IOC officials are expected to vote to award the 2034 Olympics around 3:30 a.m. local time July 24.\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2313, \"end\": 2316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9559174758450816e-15, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A live watch party is planned at the Salt Lake City and County Building in Washington Square.\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2449, \"end\": 2463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"score\": 0.9998304458197323, \"rank\": 0.00016947708244528423, \"text\": \"Salt Lake City\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salt_Lake_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Park City will be hosting its own celebration at Utah Olympic Park later in the day at 4 p.m.\", \"from\": 2506, \"to\": 2599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2506, \"end\": 2515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Olympic_Park\", \"score\": 0.9999967479300851, \"rank\": 3.252080424540809e-06, \"text\": \"Park City\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Olympic_Park\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah_Olympic_Park\"}]}]}"